Description:
Annotation on the envelope: "Rubens Kreuzaufrichtung"

- Photo of the 'Raising of the Cross'
- Extracts from different publications
- Subfolder (Annotation: "Rubens N.T. Kreuz-Aufrichtung Geplanter 'Kunstbrief' "):
   - Artworks arrangement plan
   - Draft text "Der Kreuzaufrichtungs-Altar von Peter Paul Rubens"
   - Extracts from different publications
   - Transcriptions of some Rubens' letters
- Reproduction of a drawing of St. Walburga church (Antwerp)
- Correspondence with Heise dated 1949
- Notes about some sketches in Munich (dated 1948)
- Correspondence with Th. Ruyten dated 1949
- Reproductions of the 'Raising of the Cross'
